      • getInstance

        public static DriverLicence getInstance(Name name,
                                        java.util.Date dateOfBirth,
                                        LicenceNumber licenceNumber,
                                        java.util.Date dateOfIssue,
                                        boolean isRented)
        Returns a driver licence by given information.
        参数:
        name - the name of the driver
        dateOfBirth - the date of birth of the driver
        licenceNumber - the licence number
        dateOfIssue - the date of issue of the licence
        isRented - whether the driver has rented a car
        返回:
        a driver licence by given information.
        抛出:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if name, dateOfBirth or other parameters is null
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if name, dateOfBirth or other parameters is invalid
